    <item>
      <title>拜登要求议员和捐赠者停止反对参选的行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/biden-tells-lawmakers-he-s-running-time-to-end-talk-of-swap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登试图平息民主党内围绕他的总统竞选活动的内讧，他说他决心继续参加竞选，并挑战反对者停止有关将他从选票中剔除的言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/biden-tells-lawmakers-he-s-running-time-to-end-talk-of-swap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 13:10:15 GMT</pubDate>
